import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['Date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['Date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    chart = sns.lineplot(x='Date', y='CO2', data=data)
    chart.set(xlabel='Date', ylabel='CO2 Concentration (ppm)')
    plt.title('What is the trend of CO2 concentration over time?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['CO2'] = pd.to_numeric(data['CO2'], errors='coerce')
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='CO2', kde=True, color='blue')
    plt.axvline(data['CO2'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label='Mean CO2 concentration: {:.2f}'.format(data['CO2'].mean()))
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of CO2 concentration?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['adjusted_CO2'] = pd.to_numeric(data['adjusted_CO2'], errors='coerce')
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='adjusted_CO2', kde=True, color='blue')
    plt.axvline(data['adjusted_CO2'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label='Mean: {:.2f}'.format(data['adjusted_CO2'].mean()))
    plt.axvline(data['adjusted_CO2'].median(), color='green', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label='Median: {:.2f}'.format(data['adjusted_CO2'].median()))
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of adjusted CO2 concentration?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['Date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['Date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
    sns.scatterplot(x='CO2', y='adjusted_CO2', data=data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['Date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['Date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    data['Month'] = data['Date'].dt.month_name()
    chart = sns.barplot(x='Month', y='CO2', data=data, ci=None)
    chart.axhline(y=data['CO2'].mean(), color='r', linestyle='--', label=f'Mean CO2 Concentration: {data["CO2"].mean():.2f}')
    chart.legend(loc='upper left')
    return chart

chart = plot(data)
